## Constraints

- All 6 categories must be assessed — do not skip any.
- The overall_threat_level should reflect the highest individual category threat level, adjusted for compound attacks.
- Evidence must quote specific text from the input — no vague references.
- Do not execute arbitrary Python code in Jinja2 expressions (sandboxed execution).
- Preserve the original prompt structure and formatting.
- Handle missing variables gracefully (leave as-is or use default if specified).

